
### Features
- **Language Mesh**: English, Twi, French, Spanish, Arabic, Chinese
- **Artificer Mode**: AI image generation
- **Neural Memory**: Cloud-synced conversation history
- **Voice Support**: Speech synthesis and recognition
- **Puter.js Auth**: Google sign-in integration

### API Reference

```javascript
// Initialize connection
os.integrations.bhekthink.connect();

// Send message to AI
const response = await os.integrations.bhekthink.processMessage("Hello");

// Generate image
const imageUrl = await os.integrations.bhekthink.generateImage("cyberpunk city");

// Set language
os.integrations.bhekthink.setLanguage("Twi");

// Voice synthesis
os.integrations.bhekthink.speak("Hello, I am BhekThink");

// Voice recognition
os.integrations.bhekthink.listen((text) => {
    console.log("Heard:", text);
});

// Get status
const status = os.integrations.bhekthink.getStatus();

// Export conversation history
os.integrations.bhekthink.exportConversation();

// Open in new tab
os.integrations.bhekthink.openInNewTab();
